    "Cons:",
    "- Reduces per-month revenue for annual customers by 10% (from 20% to 30% discount)",
    "- Some monthly customers will switch to annual, reducing near-term MRR (but improving predictability)",
    "",
    "Estimated impact: Convert 30% of monthly customers to annual. Reduce pricing+budget churn by 15-20%. Net revenue impact: slightly negative in Q1 2026 (as customers switch), positive by Q3 2026 (as retention improves).",
    "",
    "### Option D: AI Feature Premium Tier (Consider for Q3 2026)",
    "",
    "When AI features reach GA, introduce an 'AI' add-on at $20/seat/month for Enterprise accounts. This captures additional value from AI Search, AI Copilot, Smart Alerts, AI Agent Builder, and AI Summary.",
    "",
